    <section class="section-fade"><div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-12 lg:py-16 text-center"><h1 class="font-ibm text-[40px] sm:text-[52px] lg:text-[64px] font-normal leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em] text-cn-black mb-6">The ChowNow Blog</h1><p class="font-roboto text-[18px] lg:text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">Expert insights, strategies, and trends to help independent restaurants thrive in the digital age.</p></div></section>

