    <section class="section-fade pb-16"><div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
      <a href="#" class="blog-card block mb-12 lg:mb-16"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[16px] overflow-hidden aspect-[16/10]"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Restaurant marketing strategies" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[12px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Marketing</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[14px] text-cn-gray">8 min read</span></div><h2 class="font-ibm text-[28px] sm:text-[36px] lg:text-[42px] font-normal leading-[1.1] text-cn-black mb-4">How to Turn First-Time Customers Into Regulars: A Complete Guide</h2><p class="font-roboto text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-6">Learn proven strategies to build customer loyalty and increase repeat orders. From automated email campaigns to rewards programs, discover what works for independent restaurants.</p><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cn-blue overflow-hidden"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Author" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div><p class="font-roboto text-[14px] font-medium text-cn-black">Sarah Chen</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Jan 15, 2026</p></div></div></div></div></a>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <a href="#" class="blog-card block"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] mb-5"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Online ordering setup" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Operations</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">6 min read</span></div><h3 class="font-ibm text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.2] text-cn-black mb-3">5 Ways to Streamline Your Online Ordering Workflow</h3><p class="font-roboto text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-4">Optimize your kitchen operations and reduce errors with these proven workflow improvements.</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Jan 10, 2026</p></a>

        <a href="#" class="blog-card block"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] mb-5"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Restaurant technology" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Technology</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">10 min read</span></div><h3 class="font-ibm text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.2] text-cn-black mb-3">POS Integration 101: Why It Matters for Your Restaurant</h3><p class="font-roboto text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-4">Understand how POS integration eliminates manual entry and keeps your operations running smoothly.</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Jan 5, 2026</p></a>

        <a href="#" class="blog-card block"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] mb-5"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Third-party delivery apps" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Industry Trends</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">7 min read</span></div><h3 class="font-ibm text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.2] text-cn-black mb-3">The Hidden Costs of Third-Party Delivery Apps</h3><p class="font-roboto text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-4">Beyond commissions, discover the real impact on your brand, data, and customer relationships.</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Dec 28, 2025</p></a>

        <a href="#" class="blog-card block"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] mb-5"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Customer success story" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Customer Stories</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">5 min read</span></div><h3 class="font-ibm text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.2] text-cn-black mb-3">How Thai District Saved $300K in Commission Fees</h3><p class="font-roboto text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-4">Learn how this Los Angeles restaurant took control of their digital orders and transformed their bottom line.</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Dec 20, 2025</p></a>

        <a href="#" class="blog-card block"><div class="blog-card-img rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] mb-5"><img src="assets/placeholder.svg" alt="Restaurant email marketing" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><span class="font-ibm-cond text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cn-gray">Marketing</span><span class="text-cn-gray">•</span><span class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">9 min read</span></div><h3 class="font-ibm text-[22px] font-normal leading-[1.2] text-cn-black mb-3">Email Marketing Templates That Drive Repeat Orders</h3><p class="font-roboto text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.5] text-cn-gray mb-4">Copy and paste these proven email templates to engage customers and boost your order volume.</p><p class="font-roboto text-[13px] text-cn-gray">Dec 15, 2025</p></a>

